A RESOLUTION
1 Commending Sarah Mallett for being named Bibb County's Teacher of the Year for 2024 and
2 recognizing her exceptional contributions to education and the community; and for other
3 purposes.
4 WHEREAS, Sarah Mallett, an Audio, Video, Technology, and Film teacher at Howard
5 Middle School, has been honored as Bibb County's Teacher of the Year for 2024, reflecting
6 her dedication to excellence in teaching and her positive impact on students; and
7 WHEREAS, Ms. Mallett, a third-generation educator, has demonstrated outstanding
8 leadership and innovation in the classroom, fostering an engaging and supportive learning
9 environment that encourages student growth and achievement; and
10 WHEREAS, her classes are responsible for delivering school announcements, producing a
11 weekly newsletter, and creating video projects, providing students with valuable hands-on
12 experience in media production; and
13 WHEREAS, Ms. Mallett's personal motto, "every student that comes in knows that no matter
14 who you are, or where you come from, you have a seat at my table," exemplifies her
15 commitment to inclusivity and ensuring all students feel valued and supported; and
