16 WHEREAS, her dedication extends beyond the classroom, as she actively participates in
17 extracurricular activities and community initiatives, further enriching the educational
18 experience for her students and strengthening community ties; and
19 WHEREAS, Ms. Mallett's passion for education and unwavering commitment to her students
20 serve as an inspiration to her colleagues, students, and the broader community.
21 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
22 the members of this body recognize and commend Sarah Mallett, Bibb County's Teacher of
23 the Year for 2024, for her exemplary service as an educator and her significant contributions
24 to the academic and personal development of her students.
25 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
26 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Sarah
27 Mallett.
